posting_body: ['For leasing information call or text', 'show contact info', 'today!!!', 'Ask for ID# 3630A', 'We pamper our residents with superior service.', 'Relieve your stress in our fully equipped fitness center or immerse yourself in the tranquility of our three-and-a-half-acre lake.', 'Our long list of amenities includes a jogging trail, a park area, an island equipped with picnic tables and grills, a pool with a deck surrounding landscaped areas, access gates, lush landscaping, and a wooded natural environment.', 'We are conveniently located near several shopping malls, George Bush Intercontinental Airport, Highway 45, Beltway 8, award-winning schools, many fine restaurants, and corporate centers.', 'You are just minutes away from many exciting attractions that Houston has to offer.', 'All of our apartments come with attached garages and full-size washer and dryers.', '*select units have dual vanities.', 'We are pet-friendly so bring your furry friends along too!', 'High Speed Internet Access', 'In Unit Washer & Dryer', 'Air Conditioning', 'Heating', 'Ceiling Fans', 'Cable Ready', 'Double Vanities', 'Tub/Shower', 'Fireplace', 'Handrails', 'Sprinkler System', 'Framed Mirrors', 'Wheelchair Accessible (Rooms)', 'Kitchen Features & Appliances', 'Dishwasher', 'Disposal', 'Ice Maker', 'Granite Countertops', 'Stainless Steel Appliances', 'Pantry', 'Kitchen', 'Microwave', 'Oven', 'Range', 'Refrigerator', 'Freezer']
